description: This source file implements the MoCAHAL class methods for interacting with MoCA hardware and configuration. It includes functions for getting/setting interface configurations, retrieving status and statistics, managing associated devices, and handling ACA (Auto Channel Assessment) processes. It appears to be part of a larger project dealing with MoCA network management.

classes.name: MoCAHAL
classes.description: Main class implementing MoCA hardware and configuration interactions.

methods.name: bool initialize(IN const char * szVersion)
methods.description: Initialization function for registering the MoCAHAL wrapper.

methods.name: bool cleanup(IN const char * szVersion)
methods.description: Cleanup function for log and resource cleanup.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_GetIfConfig(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Retrieves the configuration parameters of the MoCA interface specified.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_SetIfConfig(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Sets the configuration parameters for the MoCA interface specified.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_IfGetDynamicInfo(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Gets dynamic status information of the MoCA interface.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_IfGetStaticInfo(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Retrieves static information from the MoCA node.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_IfGetStats(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Gets network layer statistics for the specified interface.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_GetNumAssociatedDevices(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Fetches number of nodes connected to the MoCA network.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_IfGetExtCounter(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Retrieves MAC layer counters at the MoCA interface.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_IfGetExtAggrCounter(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Gets aggregate data transferred (Tx & Rx) at the MoCA layer.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_GetMocaCPEs(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Obtains MAC addresses of all nodes on the MoCA network.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_GetAssociatedDevices(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Retrieves information on all associated devices/nodes.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_FreqMaskToValue(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Converts a frequency mask value to its frequency number.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_HardwareEquipped(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Checks if the MoCA hardware is equipped/enabled.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_GetFullMeshRates(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Gets the full mesh table indicating node-to-node rates.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_GetFlowStatistics(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Retrieves flow table statistics.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_GetResetCount(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Retrieves the number of MoCA resets.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_GetIfAcaConfig(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Gets the interface's ACA (Auto Channel Assessment) configuration.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_CancelIfAca(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Cancels the ongoing ACA process.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_SetIfAcaConfig(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Starts the ACA process with specified configuration.

methods.name: void MoCAHAL_GetIfAcaStatus(IN const Json::Value & req,OUT Json::Value & response)
methods.description: Retrieves the current ACA status of the interface.
